<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 06:18:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>联合国气象机构称，尽管火山喷发，臭氧层仍在恢复中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/ozone-layer-road-recovery-despite-volcano-eruption-un-weather-body-says-2024-09-17/</link><description>2022年初汤加附近的火山喷发导致去年南极洲上空的臭氧短暂加速消耗，但总体损失有限。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 05:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/ozone-layer-road-recovery-despite-volcano-eruption-un-weather-body-says-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国对抗中国的反舰武器战略：充足、机动、致命</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-strategy-anti-ship-weapons-counter-china-plentiful-mobile-deadly-2024-09-17/</link><description>美国正在积累大量且易于制造的反舰武器，作为在印太地区威慑中国和加强驻扎美军的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 05:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-strategy-anti-ship-weapons-counter-china-plentiful-mobile-deadly-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，美国和日本即将达成协议，限制对中国的芯片技术出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-japan-near-deal-curb-chip-technology-exports-china-ft-reports-2024-09-17/</link><description>英国《金融时报》周二援引知情人士的话报道称，尽管东京对北京威胁要报复日本公司发出了警告，但美国和日本即将达成协议，限制对中国芯片行业的技术出口。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 04:22:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-japan-near-deal-curb-chip-technology-exports-china-ft-reports-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>研究显示央行数字货币势头不断增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/central-bank-digital-currency-momentum-growing-study-shows-2024-09-17/</link><description>目前，占全球经济总量 98% 的 134 个国家正在探索本国货币的数字版本，其中近一半国家处于高级阶段，中国、巴哈马和尼日利亚等先驱国家的使用量开始有所增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 04:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/central-bank-digital-currency-momentum-growing-study-shows-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>俄新社报道，中国海警船抵达俄罗斯参加联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-coast-guard-ships-arrive-russia-joint-drills-ria-reports-2024-09-17/</link><description>据俄新社周二报道，中国海警船梅山号和秀山号已抵达俄罗斯远东港口符拉迪沃斯托克，与俄罗斯海警船进行联合演习和巡逻。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 02:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-coast-guard-ships-arrive-russia-joint-drills-ria-reports-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国批准向台湾出售价值约2.28亿美元的零部件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-approves-possible-military-sale-taiwan-spare-parts-about-228-mln-2024-09-17/</link><description>退回、维修和重新装运的备件将从美国政府库存中转移。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 02:11:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-approves-possible-military-sale-taiwan-spare-parts-about-228-mln-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市上涨；美元、收益率因美联储大幅降息押注而受损</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-17/</link><description>亚洲股市周二上涨，而美元和美国国债收益率承压，距离美联储宽松周期的预期开始仅剩一天，政策制定者可能会大幅降息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 01:31:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>高盛重申看涨金价，因美联储降息希望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/goldman-sachs-reiterates-bullish-view-gold-prices-amid-fed-rate-cut-hopes-2024-09-16/</link><description>高盛周一重申了对金价的乐观前景，理由是央行的需求以及美联储在本周的政策会议上即将降息。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 23:30:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/goldman-sachs-reiterates-bullish-view-gold-prices-amid-fed-rate-cut-hopes-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鸽派美联储目光，中国通货紧缩力量加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-16/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 21:48:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>帕拉西奥斯最后时刻的进球帮助艾因队在亚冠联赛中战平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/palacios-late-strike-earns-champions-al-ain-draw-asian-champions-league-2024-09-16/</link><description>周一，卫冕冠军艾因队在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛揭幕战中以 1-1 战平卡塔尔队阿尔萨德队，马蒂亚斯·帕拉西奥斯最后时刻的进球为埃尔南·克雷斯波的球队在改革后的比赛中赢得一分。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 20:51:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/palacios-late-strike-earns-champions-al-ain-draw-asian-champions-league-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>哈萨克斯坦领导人敦促肖尔茨支持中国对乌克兰的和平计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kazakh-leader-urges-scholz-support-chinas-peace-plan-ukraine-2024-09-16/</link><description>哈萨克斯坦总统托卡耶夫周一敦促来访的德国总理肖尔茨放弃俄罗斯可以在战场上被击败的想法，并支持中国对乌克兰的和平计划，但肖尔茨拒绝了这一建议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 16:48:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kazakh-leader-urges-scholz-support-chinas-peace-plan-ukraine-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>顶级商业银行加入七国集团央行主导的数字货币试验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/top-commercial-banks-join-g7-led-central-bank-digital-currency-trial-2024-09-16/</link><description>全球四十家领先的商业银行已加入由七国集团主导的试点计划，该计划与纽约联储以及欧洲、韩国和日本的主要央行合作，推出旨在加速和增强跨境支付的新数字货币平台。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 16:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/top-commercial-banks-join-g7-led-central-bank-digital-currency-trial-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>香港青年传承城市145年火龙舞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/hong-kong-youth-carry-forward-citys-145-year-old-fire-dragon-dance-2024-09-16/</link><description>周一，年轻人走上香港街头，观看具有象征意义的大坑舞火龙，希望为这一有 145 年历史的传统带来新一代。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:27:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/hong-kong-youth-carry-forward-citys-145-year-old-fire-dragon-dance-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟称中国电动汽车报价截止日期已过</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-deadline-chinese-ev-price-offers-has-passed-2024-09-16/</link><description>欧盟委员会周一表示，中国电动汽车制造商为避免关税而做出价格承诺的最后期限已经过去，在全部拒绝后，不可能修改其报价。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-deadline-chinese-ev-price-offers-has-passed-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>普京命令俄罗斯军队规模达到150万，成为仅次于中国的第二大军队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putin-orders-russian-army-grow-by-180000-soldiers-become-15-million-strong-2024-09-16/</link><description>这样的增长将使俄罗斯在可支配的现役作战士兵数量方面超越美国和印度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 12:35:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putin-orders-russian-army-grow-by-180000-soldiers-become-15-million-strong-2024-09-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>